  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fight as part of the human defiance against the relentless Machine Legion.</strong>  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick your <strong>android prototype class</strong>,<strong> </strong>experiment with powerful gear and <strong>upgrade yourself to match the Machine Gods!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471410/extras/6f798b70223bc637bee4f0b11e3062e1.poster.avif?t=1773271069\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471410/extras/6f798b70223bc637bee4f0b11e3062e1.webm?t=1773271069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471410/extras/6f798b70223bc637bee4f0b11e3062e1.mp4?t=1773271069\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1-4 Player Co-Op Mayhem</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>120+ Weapons with Deep Mechanics</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Limitless Replayability & Modding!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>▩ CO-OP MAYHEM</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight the Machine Legion <strong>Solo</strong> or in chaotic <strong>2-4 Player co-op!</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level your android classes, unlock new loadouts and experiment with new builds every run!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find powerful loot, experiment with many classes, endless load-outs and tons of crazy tech!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471410/extras/bb068cb477d9536f86b10c8bb7098719.poster.avif?t=1773271069\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471410/extras/bb068cb477d9536f86b10c8bb7098719.webm?t=1773271069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471410/extras/bb068cb477d9536f86b10c8bb7098719.mp4?t=1773271069\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>▩ NEXT LEVEL GUNPLAY</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master the satisfying <strong>manual reload</strong> system, </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >leverage the unique<strong> top-down headshots</strong>, now more accurate than ever!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A <strong>new attachment system</strong> allows for even more varied upgrade paths! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapons can now upgraded to new heights!  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapons can jam and overheat—keep your cool or burn out!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471410/extras/38e97172ff8fc7cf4ba5faa72b05d61f.poster.avif?t=1773271069\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471410/extras/38e97172ff8fc7cf4ba5faa72b05d61f.webm?t=1773271069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471410/extras/38e97172ff8fc7cf4ba5faa72b05d61f.mp4?t=1773271069\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>▩ MEET YOUR ARSENAL</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore powerful Faction Arsenals</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each weapon can come in many variants, defined by their Faction</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>▩ DEEP GAMEPLAY:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Make hard choices</strong> with expansive item and class upgrades and our unique weapon upgrades!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play either as Commando, Riotguard, Breacher, Recon, Demolisher, Machine Hunter, Chrono Trooper...</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The 10 Classes</strong> play very differently, slow, fast, tactical or brawling, choose your style! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471410/extras/1392cfe01d3341bcfdb845786a778bf2.poster.avif?t=1773271069\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471410/extras/1392cfe01d3341bcfdb845786a778bf2.webm?t=1773271069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471410/extras/1392cfe01d3341bcfdb845786a778bf2.mp4?t=1773271069\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>▩ NEXT GENERATION MODDING:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our powerful new framework, <strong>UniversEdit </strong>brings unending new possibilities for you & us! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use our truly <strong>next-level modding</strong> / content creation tools right within the game: </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Create </strong>and share your own items, abilities, weapons, classes and more <strong>within minutes</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471410/extras/5398f4d4b981555b61c8f2367538ed87.poster.avif?t=1773271069\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471410/extras/5398f4d4b981555b61c8f2367538ed87.webm?t=1773271069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471410/extras/5398f4d4b981555b61c8f2367538ed87.mp4?t=1773271069\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>▧ NEW IN SYNTHETIK 2 - vs - SYNTHETIK 1:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 Player co-op unleashes complete mayhem!  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore more and <strong>more varied  environments</strong> with destruction, physics & <strong>full 3D</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight the <strong>Machine S.A.T Police Force</strong>,<strong> Chrono Squad and Machine Military </strong>and their bosses!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The now <strong>10 Classes</strong> play more differently, slow, fast, tactical or brawling, choose your style!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master new mechanics such as <strong>single shell reload</strong>, <strong>dual wield</strong> and more!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A deeper, tailored <strong>attachment and item upgrade</strong> system allow for more customization than ever!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Armor 2.0</strong> enables rear-armor hits, deflections, ricochets and more realistic gunplay!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The new Difficulty <strong>Directives</strong> System allows adding new enemies or other powerful challenges!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create new Classes, Items and Weapons with ease with <strong>UniversEdit!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Other Improvements:</strong></h2></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Power Slots</strong> - all items can either be set to automatic or manually activated!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Weapon Technologies</strong> - All weapons come with randomized technology-based perks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Faction Variants</strong> - Each weapon faction has their own set of unique variants!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471410/extras/2b323caa9cfbcfb87923a40cd8b9a7d5.poster.avif?t=1773271069\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471410/extras/2b323caa9cfbcfb87923a40cd8b9a7d5.webm?t=1773271069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1471410/extras/2b323caa9cfbcfb87923a40cd8b9a7d5.mp4?t=1773271069\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
